text: Is RecurSat going to be open Source at some point?

elements.text: Is RecurSat going to be open Source at some point?

text: I hope I can and I’m going to try to get it there. There’s nothing contractor proprietary about it, so there should be no issue with that. And I don’t think it will have any problems related to ITAR restrictions either. The only thing is just going through the approval process, which can take a few months. So we’ll see there. I’ll keep everyone updated.
